This indicated that the change in body composition was likely due to 
hyperphagia. 
We next performed an intraperitoneal glucose tolerance test (GTT). A 
2-way mixed model with repeated measures (2w-ANOVA) revealed a 
main effect of housing (*p = 0.0113, F (1, 18) = 7.970), and a housing x 
